---
title: "The Second Batch of New Hymns!"
author: "Joey Stanley"
date: "2024-09-18"
date-modified: last-modified
categories: 
  - general
  - frequency
  - new hymns
reference-location: margin
---











On September 12th, the church released the second batch of new hymns. In [a previous post](/posts/new_hymns_batch1), I covered in detail as much as I could about the first batch of hymns and how they rolled out between June 2 and September 8th. This page covers period between when the second batch came out and when the third batch will come out, whenever that will be and will update regularly as I collect more data. Currently I have data from 6,407 sacrament meetings since September 15th from 1,362 wards.

But first, here's how much data I have for each week, just so you have an idea of what I'm working with. I have collected more data per week from the past few months than from any other time period in my dataset.



